FBIS4-16065 "drsov072_m_94001" FBIS-SOV-94-072 Daily Report 13 Apr 1994 Tajikistan Militants Surround Russian Border Guards Militants Surround Russian Border Guards LD1304124494 Moscow Ostankino Television First Channel Network in Russian 1100 GMT 13 Apr 94 LD1304124494 Moscow Ostankino Television First Channel Network Russian BFN [From the "Novosti" newscast] [Text] INTERFAX has learned that a group of Tajik militants surrounded a convoy of lorries of Russian border guards near the 7th outpost of the Khorogskiy border district, demanding weapons and ammunition. Russian border guards have refused to comply with the demands of the militants and are at present conducting negotiations to end this conflict peacefully.
